metadata.description:
Disassembled symbolizes a triadic paradox of femininity, manifesting the archetypes of maiden, mother, and crone. Each figure embodies a phase of the feminine journey, reflecting the lifecycle in their mystical communion.

Created for the AI Surrealism exhibition at Oculus NYC, hosted by Superchief Gallery NFT and Exquisite Workers. The largest AI art show in history, featuring 100 AI artists, June 2-8, 2023. Curated by Anna Dart and Roger Haus.
